name: Elexis Sinclaire
description:
From the official (of the very few, official or not) cosplay from the E3 2006 showing of Sin Episodes, with the lovely Bianca Beauchamp.

Includes the standard jacket and pants look: "esjacket"

And the bikini: "esbikini"

And with lower number, and just the esjacket/esbikini, you can cosplay the cosplay. Reducing the esjacket strength makes some nice outfits too.
